HEADWORD: Amphistomous
<hw>Am*phis"to*mous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'amfi`</grk> + <?/ mouth.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having a
